&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">Max charging voltage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">4289539&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c">#当前充电电压， 这里为 4289539 nV 纳伏特 换算为 4.289539 mV&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
